NAME

DateTime::Locale::so - Locale data examples for the Somali (so) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Somali locale.

Date Formats

Full

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = Talaado, Bisha Labaad 05, 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Jimco, Bisha Laba iyo Tobnaad 22, 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Sabti, Bisha Sagaalaad 15, -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 05 Bisha Labaad 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Bisha Laba iyo Tobnaad 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Bisha Sagaalaad -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 05-Feb-2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22-Dis-1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15-Seb--10

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 05/02/08
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22/12/95
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15/09/-10
